Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸腐于野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊断于利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱之人 且赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国千代少爷 您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国千代少爷 请振作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国千代少爷 国千代少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了 阿江与夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人对国千代少爷下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然幸好少爷已无大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能就此罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事应该立刻通知骏府的家康大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请夫人三思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是为继承人一事纠缠不清的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,息事宁人 耐心等待才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 天海大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真勇猛啊 竹千代少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话请别忘了对那只不在场的狐狸精说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺 弦之介吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎 你带弦之介大人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 请您看清世间之理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着 小四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰啊 你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用振翅之音告诉我敌人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被弦之介大人所伤的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是看不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再看一次那幅景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会从哪里袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我吗 弹正大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这是何人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他身上母亲的血统…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐的血统显得更浓一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我训练他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教他你的瞳术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要他变强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比老夫更强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得太清楚的眼也并非是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个直率的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好听的声音呢 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要鸟的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不解风情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也该多少习些风雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知故问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些 我想学的是你的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样蒙着眼睛 整天奔走在卍谷的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您讨厌散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想变强 为了甲贺 以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样怎么能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若知道你会用瞳术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人首先会攻击你的双眼 这是兵法的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了应付万一双目被封时的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要应付万一 快教我瞳术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续走 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨锐五感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 这种山路根本不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有点危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告诉您很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是胆怯会更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界复杂离奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切事物相互交错 不断变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看清主宰混沌之世的事理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的双目便能捕捉万物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我瞳术的真谛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是世间万物之理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事理是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是明白的话就不用辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹正大人没有看走眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人的确身怀瞳术的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有正必有邪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有美丽的事物 也有丑陋的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同时接纳这两者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人的眼睛太过率直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不需要会让那双眼瞳阴翳的事理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 您感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:17:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿掉眼罩看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见 豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是世间之理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亮闪闪的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太阳 不仅照耀甲贺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也同样照耀着伊贺鍔隐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是世间之理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是世间之理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…活下去…弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有击中目标的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却没有倒下的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 的确应该是得手了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿 甲贺的家伙 藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎他们回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 鹰的状况非同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非天膳大人和小四郎阁下出了什么意外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿 到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没时间浪费在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…我必须保护胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶快…赶快回胧小姐身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱绢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.41,name,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,35)\fad(300,300)\frz-90}德川竹千代乳母 阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱幻影倒下的双镰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子的悲吟第一次溢出胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖气蒸腾的月下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自死亡的泥沼中鼓动的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎风而现的高大女中豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今将在此揭开甲贺伊贺双方的真意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Basilisk 甲贺忍法帖
